          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The 24Na and 28Mg radionuclides have been detected  by",
                " their   gamma-activity   using   radiochemistry.  The",
                " purified Th-targets were activated by  bremsstrahlung",
                " at end-point energies  E-E  =  12, 16.5, and  24 MeV.",
                " Possible backgrounds are carefully analyzed,  and the",
                " yields of the light nuclei have been found on a level",
                " of 10**(-6) per fission event."
              ]
            }
          ],
